    Function reference

    Leaflet.Circle-sector wrappers

    Wrapper functions for the Leaflet plugin “Leaflet.Circle-sector”.

    addCircleSectorMid()
    Add Circle sectors to a Leaflet map from a dataframe using bearing and spread
    addCircleSectorMinMax()
    Add Circle sectors to a Leaflet map from a dataframe using start and end angles
    circlePlugin()
    Register htmlDependency for leaflet.circle-sector.js
    leaflet_basemap()
    Create a Leaflet basemap focused on Western Australia
    registerPlugin()
    A pipe-friendly way to register a plugin for a Leaflet map

    Example data

    Packaged example data.

    fans
    Turtle hatchling nest emergences: Main fan of tracks
    fans_mean
    A data frame ready to be used in addCircleSectorMid
    fans_tracks
    A data frame ready to be used in addCircleSectorMinMax
    fans_water
    A data frame ready to be used in addCircleSectorMid
    light_segments_artificial
    A data frame ready to be used in addCircleSectorMid
    light_segments_natural
    A data frame ready to be used in addCircleSectorMid
    lights
    Turtle hatchling nest emergences: Known light sources
    outlier_segments
    A data frame ready to be used in addCircleSectorMid
    outliers
    Turtle hatchling nest emergences: Individual outlier tracks
